{"tid":2138672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【港版國安法】繼德國之後 法國宣佈中止與港引渡協議","createTime":"2020-08-03T17:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T03:23:18.000Z","uid":320680,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"996582a523612d6e3e7ef1c49796c560adca98aa","tid":2138672,"uid":320680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200803/QWB7PLYT6WW7NQI2EP25XWRACQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200803%2FQWB7PLYT6WW7NQI2EP25XWRACQ%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=3a782c9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200803%2FQWB7PLYT6WW7NQI2EP25XWRACQ%2F&h=2e45264a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200803/QWB7PLYT6WW7NQI2EP25XWRACQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90eda50f7eaa426664a2c17c37cfd50af8134171","tid":2138672,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T21:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb115a0a2b6ddc4671082627a4175b55e481275","tid":2138672,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:15:57.000Z","msg":"法國外交部周一發表聲明，宣佈暫停與香港的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n聲名指，鑑於最新發展，法國不會繼續承認2017年5月4日與港簽署的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法實施，西方國家迴響極大，多國宣佈中止與港引渡協議，包括情報聯盟「五眼聯盟」中的英國、加拿大、澳洲、新西蘭。美國總統特朗普上月簽署《香港自治法案》（Hong Kong Autonomy Act），可對實施港區國安法的中國官員與金融機構祭出制裁與簽證限制，並表明有意中止與港引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟上周二發聲明，對港版國安法之實施表示嚴重關切，同意限制向香港出口用於鎮壓及監視的設備。成員國中，德國上周已宣佈暫停與港引渡協議。<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"ac40fcc515bdf2ce019412bb1d7e79217a8a26fa","tid":2138672,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d24135867768d67a0a8d31fde857a323f03bac7","tid":2138672,"uid":342855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:31:35.000Z","msg":"港共又要準備定template了"},{"pid":"c920f7d7de19931f53f10c3a2f578ff21d2e1b13","tid":2138672,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y67nE1z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy67nE1z.png&h=d5dc35a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"018579f89b85fbb33d1cb60a54d885fd42447a35","tid":2138672,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"中共：要求法國向法治交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca673b76277caf2f993ea6e6ca8ba2660590e1c","tid":2138672,"uid":16707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"法國同香港簽咗但未生效就宣佈暫停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}